---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

import company from '../data/company.json';
import social from '../data/social.json';
---

<PageLayout title='Projects' description=`Software projects developed by ${company.name}.`>
	<Fragment slot="page-header">Projects</Fragment>
	<article slot="page-content">
		<p>We develop all kinds of software projects, typically related to games. These are tools we use and want to freely share with others. You can check some of them out on our <a href={social.githubURL}>GitHub</a>.</p>
		<h2>Wiki Projects</h2>
		<h3><a href=`https://soulsborne.wiki`>The Soulsborne Wikis</a></h3>
		<p>A set of independent community-focused wikis for all major Soulsborne titles. This website is a passion project run by us and the community to provide a valuable resource for a community we love.</p>
		<h3><a href=`https://dragcave.wiki`>The Dragon Cave Wiki</a></h3>
		<p>An independent community-focused wiki for <a href=`https://dragcave.net`>Dragon Cave</a>. Like the Soulsborne Wikis, this website is a passion project run by us and the community to provide a valuable resource for a community we love.</p>
		<h2>Site Projects</h2>
		<h3><a href=`https://runekit.com/`>Runekit</a></h3>
		<p>A set of utilities and tools for RuneScape. <i>(Currently under construction.)</i></p>
		<h2>Utilities, Tools, and Libraries</h2>
		<h3><a href=`https://github.com/adelheidsoftware/godot-utilities`>Godot Utilities</a></h3>
		<p>A set of utilities we maintain for our games, available in a variety of languages, such as GDScript and C#.</p>
